Hi there!

Press a button on your mouse or gamepad to join (and jump).
You can jump in the air as well!
You can push orange blocks like this if you want.

The counter shows your remaining jumps.
It recharges with time.

You need to fling the balls to the exit on the right.

Use your magnetic superpowers!
‚Üê This is the exit. And here's your target ‚Üí

You are invincible, but
red shapes will destroy balls.

Aim with the mouse or the left analog stick.
If you have friends around, they can join to.

If you get stuck, press R
or Start/Menu on your gamepad
to restart the level.
Blue ones are heavy and stiff.
Pink ones are light and bouncy.
We T-3'd this jam (again), but we promise to add more levels soon ;)
